# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# AidPulse SG — environment template
#
# SETUP (every teammate, on every machine):
#   1. Copy this file to ".env.local"  (cp .env.example .env.local)
#   2. Fill in the real values below (your team lead shares the Twilio secrets
#      out-of-band — password manager / DM, NEVER in git or a screenshot).
#   3. Restart the dev server — env vars only load at startup:  npm run dev
#
# ".env.local" is gitignored on purpose so secrets never reach GitHub.
# Only THIS file (.env.example, placeholders only) is committed.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# n8n Webhook node "Production URL" — the chatbot forwards messages here.
N8N_WEBHOOK_URL=https://your-n8n-instance.app.n8n.cloud/webhook/aidpulse-chat

# Supabase — powers the live citizen dashboard (case stats, area ranking, news).
# Settings → API → Project URL + anon/publishable key. The anon key is
# client-safe (it ships to the browser), so it's fine to share with the team.
# Leave blank to run on mock/empty data (the app won't crash either way).
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=sb_publishable_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

# ─── Twilio Verify (real SMS OTP on citizen sign-up) ────────────────────────
# Twilio Console → Account Info: Account SID + Auth Token.
# Verify → Services: create a Verify Service to get its SID (starts "VA...").
#
# IMPORTANT — to get a REAL SMS delivered:
#   • On a Twilio TRIAL account, the destination number must be added under
#     Phone Numbers → Verified Caller IDs, OR upgrade the account to remove
#     that restriction.
#   • Enable the destination country under Messaging → Geo Permissions
#     (e.g. Singapore), or the SMS fails silently.
#
# The TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN is a real secret. If it ever leaks, rotate it in the
# Twilio Console immediately. Leave these blank to keep OTP disabled (the
# sign-up shows a clear "not configured" message instead of crashing).
TWILIO_ACCOUNT_SID=ACxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=your_twilio_auth_token_here
TWILIO_VERIFY_SERVICE_SID=VAxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx
